Stanli 

install First 

	sudo apt install steghide -y 
	
To emmbed a file or message to a image we use this command 

	steghide embed -cf input.jpg -ef secret.txt

To retrive or see the message from a file we use this command 

	steghide extract -sf input.jpg



Flag-by-Flag Breakdown:

Flag		Full Form				Meaning in Hindi (Hinglish Style)

-cf			cover file				Image/audio file jisme secret data chhupana hai (e.g., cover.jpg)
-ef			embed file				Woh file jisko chhupana hai (e.g., secret.txt, virus.exe)
-sf			stego file				Jisme data chhupa hua hai, use extract karne ke liye diya jata hai
-p			passphrase				Password set ya use karne ke liye (optional, but safer)
-xf			extract file			Extracted file ka naam specify karne ke liye (optional)




